INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES("1241", "522", "panels_data", "a:3:{s:7:\"widgets\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"text\";s:2620:\"<p>Rewind about 6 months and my life would now seem unrecognizable. I was feeling tired, broke and listless. I had no motivation and felt like my life was stuck in an endless cycle of work, sleep, and paying bills. Since I cook for a living, I would often end up eating leftovers every night. Then one day, I came home from work to find my fiancee full of excitement about a new opportunity she had discovered. At the time, my conditioned response would have been skepticism and doubt. Her excitement was strong, however, and I couldn\'t help but catch on to it. So I sat down and looked at the opportunity and, in a moment of boldness uncharacteristic for me at the time, decided to take action. My life changed forever that night.</p><p>What happened to me is called a paradigm shift. Basically I experienced a change in perspective that allowed me to see my situation in a different light. I suddenly began realizing that the reason I felt like I was stuck in my life was because I wasn\'t changing my actions to get different results. I had been blind to the fact that as long as I kept simply going to work for my paycheck and stressing out about it so much that I had no time to pursue, or even think about what my dreams were or how to achieve them. I was stuck in a rut, but it wasn\'t due to my circumstances, it was because I kept doing the same thing every day.</p><p>My fiancee and I have seen our lives accelerate in a way neither of us would have thought possible previously. I still have the same job, the same car, and the same apartment, yet we are happier, more motivated and more fulfilled in all aspects of life because of our paradigm shift. By consciously choosing to admit our responsibility for our situation, shift our perspective, and take action, we have been able to attract a much more abundant life. Simply by focusing on how we desired our lives to be, rather than how hard things were, our desires began to appear all around us. We began to have extra money at the end of each paycheck, even enough to invest a little. The financing for our business came through. I got a big raise at work and Meg got a job working from home. Now if we want to grab some takeout so we don\'t have to cook every night, we don\'t even worry if we can afford it. We know we can.</p><p>So there you have it. With a simple change in perspective, we have been able to shift into high gear and accelerate our lives. If you are feeling bad about the way things are going, try changing your paradigm and see yourself at your best. See yourself as the victorious you that we all know you are and you will become it.</p>\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:6:\"visual\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:5:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;}}i:1;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:225:\"<p>[spacer height=\"20px\"]</p><center><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/w9HQFNe85yA\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></center><center>[spacer height=\"20px\"]</center>\";s:20:\"text_selected_editor\";s:4:\"tmce\";s:5:\"autop\";b:1;s:12:\"_sow_form_id\";s:13:\"572577cc32edc\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:31:\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}}s:5:\"grids\";a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"cells\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:0:{}}}s:10:\"grid_cells\";a:2:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:6:\"weight\";i:1;}i:1;a:2:{s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:6:\"weight\";i:1;}}}");
